title: Hour 1: What Is The Cost Of Greatness?
description:
Stugotz tells us how he feels after the Braves officially clinched the NL East over his Mets and we discuss Tom Brady and Gisele Bundchen’s divorce playing out publicly. Then, Chelsea Handler joins to discuss getting back on the road, a potential return to late night TV, and dating during the pandemic.
